gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Clippers 117, Jazz 103
gameRecap.excerpt: The Clippers defeated the Jazz, 117-103. Kawhi Leonard recorded a new season-high 41 points (6-8 3PM) along with five rebounds and five assists for the Clippers. Paul George added 20 points, three rebounds, and three assists in the victory. John Collins tallied 20 points and 13 rebounds for the Jazz in the losing effort. The Clippers improve to 11-10 in the regular season, while the Jazz fall to 7-15.
